News.Title: Moksh Ornaments Secures Major Order from Lalithaa Jewellery Mart
News.Summary: Moksh Ornaments has received a significant new order worth Rs 120 crore from Lalithaa Jewellery Mart. The company is planning to expand its product range and enter international markets in the coming months. Moksh Ornaments currently has a market capitalization of Rs 118 crore.
